Responsive Design - The interface adjusts to the screen size no matter how big or how small

Grid based design - Web design with grid content

Media Queries - Break Points
Common - Desktop, Mobile, Tablet
- Usually around 600 px

Em usually used for font size

Px = Static measurement
Em = Adjust to its parent
Em for responsive design
Px for non responsive design
em is unit of measure in CSS

How to convert px to em - Multiply by 1.5

pseudo class selector - use to define a special state
common - focus, hover